items.title: Netzer collects two hits for Greenville
items.summary: The Tulsa Drillers slugged their way to another playoff victory on Wednesday, as Drew Jackson and Matt Beaty collected a combined five hits, including three extra-base hits, in a 5-4 win over Midland in Game 2 of the Texas League finals.
